comments.body: At some point we should find a way to make sure that the advertised K8S version for these test images is the actual K8S version it was built with.

@@ -1,1 +15,19 @@build:
	CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -o webhook .
	docker build --no-cache -t gcr.io/kubernetes-e2e-test-images/k8s-sample-admission-webhook-amd64:1.9v1 .
	rm -rf webhook
